  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  npcName: Aria
  dialogueLines:
  - I have heard about this mural before. The saying goes like this...
  - '"Everything started in the center, from there it spread to the north and then
    to the south."'
  - '"When it comes to things you don''t know, you should keep your hands off them."'
  - '"Beginning and end? Pff. What really matters is first who is on top and second
    who is on the bottom."'
  - '"In the end, you always find the middle. First the right one, then the left
    one."'
  interactionSound: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 92368ab2d65903c4aa971b7ce4178240, type: 3}
