  - {fileID: 194038135}
  playableDirector: {fileID: 436287870}
  dialogLines:
  - Hey Aya, did you see that all the gates in the light kingdom are sealed?
  - "I heard rumours about the king of all god\u2019s vanished and very powerful
    artefacts were stolen from his chamber."
  - "But i can contact my friends from other kingdoms to get more information\u2026"
  - Maybe if you talk to people in town, they might know more details.
  - "I\u2019ll talk to you later Aya.\n"
